node.text:
“Once upon a time a dress so fine…”
16 artists from around the world, distilled into one vision for the Maison’s latest Haute Couture show. Discover the Valentino Des Ateliers Backstage Story, an exploration into the process and symbiotic relationship between painters and Valentino’s Creative Director, Pierpaolo Piccioli.

Words and concept by GLR
Filming and editing by @ginevraag 
Music: Goldfinch- Flight to the north

node.text:
Fashion is linked to the body and to movement.
Art, however, is completely free from constraint.
@pppiccioli’s latest #ValentinoHauteCouture show, #ValentinoDesAteliers, brings art into conversation with fashion, transmuting surfaces, animating works into motion.
Experience the entire collection, shown this evening in Venice’s Gaggiandre, Arsenale, and set to the sounds of @cos1ma.

In the latest chapter of Valentino’s “Mastery Tales,” the process behind a special Valentino Garavani #RomanStud Top Handle is unveiled.

Made specifically for the Valentino Garavani 520 Capsule Collection, the bag features 5 studs on each side and 20 total to create a symbol of love and care, just in time for China’s 520 Day. Shop the bag in a special blue color along with red, white, black and pink on Valentino.cn, or by visiting Valentino Tmall Luxury Pavillion, WeChat or Valentino China boutiques.
